    "title": "Use of deprecated CryptAcquireContext in random.cpp",
    "body": "According to [Windows API documentation](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/win32/api/wincrypt/nf-wincrypt-cryptacquirecontextw), the `CryptAcquireContext*` function along with `CryptGenRandom` as used in `src/random.cpp` is deprecated:\n\n> Important  This API is deprecated. New and existing software should start using [Cryptography Next Generation APIs.](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/desktop/SecCNG/cng-portal) Microsoft may remove this API in future releases.\n\n",
